 (15, 'Typescript: Interface', 'JIn this article, you''ll learn about what interface are and how to use them, along with the difference between type and interface. This article gives you a basic understanding of the interface.', 
    '<p style="margin: 0 0 var(--content-rhythm) 0; color: rgb(23, 23, 23); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 20px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;">In this article, you''ll learn about what&nbsp;interface are and how to use them, along with the difference between type&nbsp;and&nbsp;interface. This article gives you a basic understanding of the interface.</p><blockquote style="margin: 0 0 var(--content-rhythm) 0; border-left: 4px solid var(--base-20); padding: 0 0 0 var(--content-rhythm); color: rgb(23, 23, 23); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 20px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;"><p style="margin: 0 0 var(--content-rhythm) 0;">This is going to be a full series of typescript where you will learn from basic topics like string, boolean to more complex like Type Aliases, enums, Interface, generics, and etc.</p></blockquote><h3 style="margin: calc(var(--content-rhythm) / 2) 0; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-weight: var(--fw-bold); line-height: var(--lh-tight); font-size: 1.25em; color: rgb(23, 23, 23); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal;"><a name="table-of-contents" href="https://dev.to/j471n/typescript-interface-3748?ref=dailydev#table-of-contents" style="color: var(--link-branded-color); text-decoration-line: underline;"></a>Table of Contents</h3><ul style="padding-left: var(--su-6); margi